data.title: The best stand-up comedy in Southern Indiana
data.text: This was a small place but the drinks were great and the comedians were awesome. This was our first time there.  I was laughing so hard that I couldn't catch my breathe. The staff was exceptionally friendly.  The crowd was great. I would recommend this place to anyone who is visiting Evansville and all the locals.  Much better than going to the casino!
